title: HOW WE PICKED OUR BABIES' NAMES | BABY GIRL COMES HOME FROM THE NICU
author: Lauren & Arie
description:
Our girl is home! Lauren surprises Arie and brings baby girl home from the nicu. Plus since we had so many questions about the twins names we wanted to share how we came up with them! Make sure to SUBSCRIBE to show us some love!

If you haven't seen these videos, check them out... 

Meet our babies! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yXXH__JSGrk&t=14s 
Finding out we're having twins! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mr5Ym...
Pregnancy announcement: https://youtu.be/2Up7Jbtg37A 
Twin Pregnancy Q&A: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BjUZA...

Follow us on Instagram too!
https://www.instagram.com/laurenluyendyk
https://www.instagram.com/ariejr
https://www.instagram.com/alessiluyendyk

As always, we love and appreciate every one of you!

-Lauren and Arie Luyendyk
